        android:textSize="15dp"
        android:textColor="#000000"
        android:text="   By 2017, 45% of mobile cloud services will be software as a service (SaaS)-based solutions.   Business usersâ€™ demands are already driving greater requirements for cloud-based mobile applications beyond messaging or relatively simple contact management and sales force automation systems (SFA)."
